        {
            "title": "Roku股價飆升20%，傳出公司正洽談潛在出售事宜",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MCv2PoKFEDjJO_UE0jWW3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE49167_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 流媒體平台公司Roku Inc.（納斯達克：ROKU）股價週五大漲逾20%，此前彭博社報道稱，該公司已與至少一家美國媒體公司就潛在出售事宜展開磋商。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博社引述知情人士透露，這家總部位於加州聖荷西的公司正就可能的合併方案進行洽談。消息人士表示，目前尚未作出任何最終決定，相關討論亦未必會促成實際交易。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Roku發言人未有就上述報道即時回應置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在傳統媒體巨頭與科技龍頭企業競相爭奪流媒體市場份額的激烈競爭格局下，Roku一直在積極尋求突破。該公司旗下平台透過自家硬件設備及軟件，讓用戶得以便捷地訪問各類流媒體服務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/roku%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%8720-%E5%82%B3%E5%87%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%AD%A3%E6%B4%BD%E8%AB%87%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C-202026032.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-13 04:28:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國應急儲備原油出口飆升至歷史新高 戰爭擾亂供應",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"DOE data compiled by Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"662\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kVPykW_5A9OHCtKnV8nZPg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fd2bffcb3f0159f0a742dddaa517ffcb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">DOE data compiled by Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由於伊朗戰爭引發有記錄以來最嚴重的供應中斷，美國應急儲備原油出口飆升至歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kpler Ltd.匯編的海關數據顯示，今年迄今已有近2,200萬桶來自美國戰略石油儲備(SPR)的原油銷往海外市場。這一規模已超過四年前創下的前高，當時俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭後，大量儲備原油被釋放。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"744\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xh8A3ac2Q80OkBUTkLRkmQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc0NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/30f58e75bab2e3a7d8149e65493680f8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管美國應急儲備原油出口並不罕見，但今年出貨規模之大顯示，隨著霍爾木茲海峽近乎關閉引發供應中斷，全球市場正愈發依賴美國供應來渡過難關。從應急儲備庫流出的原油中，每三桶就有大約一桶出口。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2ba7ec24-465b-3707-bbc3-3ea0f346a92d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">流向海外的數量可能還會更高，因為川普政府仍在釋放所承諾的全部1.72億桶原油。這是國際能源署(IEA)更大規模行動的一部分，旨在幫助緩衝伊朗戰爭對全球能源市場的影響。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">出口原油中的大部分，或90%，目的地是歐洲，流向荷蘭，也首次流向希臘、保加利亞和土耳其的煉油商。至少有一船貨正在駛往亞洲。超級油輪Arosa裝載120萬桶Bryan Mound Sour原油，顯示目的地為菲律賓巴丹。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"662\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kPUqlUh9nro7vOdkw59kpA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6fd65e9dbe4339fca3b39b4f1a1b71b5\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大宗商品貿易商托克集團已成為SPR原油的最大買家，其次是煉油商Marathon Petroleum Corp和殼牌的交易部門。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著供應繼續出庫，庫存正迅速逼近上世紀80年代以來的最低水平。在汽油價格居高不下之際，這引發了對美國國內能源安全的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">補庫最早可能在9月開始，根據置換計畫，屆時貿易商和煉油商將開始歸還從儲備中借出的原油。政府計畫借出1.72億桶原油，換回約2億桶原油。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump’s Emergency Oil Flows Overseas at a Record Pace on War</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%87%89%E6%80%A5%E5%84%B2%E5%82%99%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E6%93%BE%E4%BA%82%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89-190530882.html",
